Package com.kapoorlabs.kiara.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ColumnNotFoundException
    This exception is raised at time of search, when the column specified in query is not found in the store.
    EmptyColumnException
    This exception is raised at loadtime when we try to build a store with no eligible columns.
    IndexingException
    This exception is raised during index creation of load time, if there is bad data, such conditions can occur, for example an invalid Range.
    InsufficientDataException
    This exception is raised during search time, when between operator is used in a condition and both lower and upper ranges are not specified.
    LoadDataException
    This exception is raised during load time, when we try to load an object that does not match the class(based on which the store was created),or it has an inaccessible private getter method.
    NonSupportedOperationException
    This exception is raised during search time, if any operator other than EQUALS ,CONTAINS_EITHER or CONTAINS_ALL is used in range based data, OR, if the operator NOT_CONTAINS is used for single data type columns.
    RangeOutOfOrderException
    This exception is raised both at loadtime and searchtime when we try to parse a range with higher range value, which is less than lower range.
    UnknownRangeFormatException
    This exception is raised both at loadtime and search time for datetime/date based ranges when the length of the range does not match the date's format length.
